\begin_layout Enumerate
It may be useful to include a new variable, the wet-equivalent potential
 temperature 
\begin_inset Formula $\Theta_{q}$
\end_inset

, in the data files.
 This is easier to calculate and less controversial than 
\begin_inset Formula $\Theta_{p}$
\end_inset

